</p>
<p>2013. Available from http://embassies.gov.il/UnGeneva/NewsAndEvents/Pages/Autopsy-on-
Palestinian-detainee-Arafat-Jaradat.aspx. 
</p>
<p> 23 www.alhaq.org/images/stories/PDF/2012/Arafat_Jaradat.pdf.  
